vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for and a resolution accepting an amendment to existing deed restrictions [Z978-150] volunteered by the applicant, on property zoned a CS Commercial Service District, on the northeast side of South Fitzhugh Avenue, north of South Haskell Avenue
Recommendation of Staff and CPC:  Approval, subject to amended deed restrictions volunteered by the applicant
Z190-168(JM)
Note: This item was deferred by the City Council before opening the public hearing on May 13, 2020, and is scheduled for consideration on May 27, 2020
